				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-2afc67b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="2afc67b" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix"><p>My main research interests are in <strong>Data Management and Algorithms</strong>, specifically <strong>Accountability and Transparency of Algorithms for Decision-Making</strong>, <strong>Explainable Rankings,</strong> <strong>Personal Information Management</strong>, <strong>Data Integration</strong>, and <strong>Data Corroboration</strong>.</p></div>
